  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/c7340aa450a9e9152353ba3b3cb62389.poster.avif?t=1685216157\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/c7340aa450a9e9152353ba3b3cb62389.webm?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/c7340aa450a9e9152353ba3b3cb62389.mp4?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A king under threat. A great power hangs in the balance. After uncovering a regicidal plot, the old Mage must leverage the forbidden power of mind/body dualism to cross dimensions, possess the bodies of others and ultimately foil the assassination plot on the King whom he serves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/f95a8ebef9268f5fd3bd2f39b2af2e1a.poster.avif?t=1685216157\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/f95a8ebef9268f5fd3bd2f39b2af2e1a.webm?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/f95a8ebef9268f5fd3bd2f39b2af2e1a.mp4?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Solve problems, overcome obstacles and explore to uncover the mystery in this arcade-style 2D puzzle-platformer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/40810d7445361be58b081345b55ed778.poster.avif?t=1685216157\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/40810d7445361be58b081345b55ed778.webm?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/40810d7445361be58b081345b55ed778.mp4?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each level offers its own unique challenges, from tricky obstacles to exciting puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/d1b121706c56934899da576045fc021f.poster.avif?t=1685216157\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/d1b121706c56934899da576045fc021f.webm?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908080/extras/d1b121706c56934899da576045fc021f.mp4?t=1685216157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Will you make the right decisions and achieve a happy ending, or will your choices lead to a darker fate?",
